    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩於已滅度諸佛世尊及諸弟子功德善根，若欲發起隨喜迴向無上正等菩提心者，應作是念：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『如佛世尊及諸弟子皆已滅度自性非有，功德善根亦復如是。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我所發起隨喜迴向無上正等菩提之心，及所迴向無上菩提，性相亦爾都不可得。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』如是知已，於諸善根發生隨喜迴向無上正等菩提，便能不生想心見倒，名正隨喜迴向菩提。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a09_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩以取相為方便，行深般若波羅蜜多，於已滅度佛及弟子功德善根，取相隨喜迴向菩提，是為非善隨喜迴向，由斯便墮想心見倒。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a12_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩不取相為方便，行深般若波羅蜜多，於已滅度佛及弟子功德善根，離相隨喜迴向無上正等菩提，是名為善隨喜迴向，由斯不墮想心見倒。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，慈氏菩薩摩訶薩問具壽善現言：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大德！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a17_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何菩薩摩訶薩於諸如來、應、正等覺及弟子眾功德善根、隨喜俱行福業事等皆不取相，而能隨喜迴向無上正等菩提？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」善現答言：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a20_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「應知菩薩摩訶薩所學般若波羅蜜多，有如是等方便善巧，雖不取相而所作成，非離般若波羅蜜多，有能正起隨喜迴向。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故菩薩摩訶薩眾欲成所作，應學般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」慈氏菩薩摩訶薩言：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大德善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "莫作是說。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a25_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以甚深般若波羅蜜多中，諸佛世尊并弟子眾及所成就功德善根，皆無所有都不可得，所作隨喜諸福業事、發心迴向無上菩提，亦無所有都不可得。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794a29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此中菩薩摩訶薩行深般若波羅蜜多時，應作是觀：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "過去諸佛及弟子眾功德善根性皆已滅，所作隨喜諸福業事、發心迴向無上菩提性皆寂滅。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我若於彼諸佛世尊及弟子眾功德善根取相分別，及於所作隨喜俱行諸福業事、發心迴向無上菩提取相分別，以是取相分別方便，發生隨喜迴向無上正等菩提，諸佛世尊皆所不許。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於已滅度諸佛世尊及弟子等取相分別，隨喜迴向無上菩提，是則名為大有所得。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "過去已滅，無所有故，未來、現在佛弟子等未至、不住，亦不可得。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b11_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不可得非取相境，若取其相發生隨喜迴向菩提便墮顛倒。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有失念而取相者，當知非善隨喜迴向，要不取相無所分別，乃名為善隨喜迴向。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b14_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是故菩薩摩訶薩眾應學般若波羅蜜多方便善巧，由此方便善巧勢力，能正發生隨喜迴向。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩欲學如是方便善巧，應於般若波羅蜜多數數聽聞、受持、讀誦，令善通利、如理思惟，勤請問師甚深義趣。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b19_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不依止甚深般若波羅蜜多，終不能得方便善巧。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無如是方便善巧，能正發生隨喜迴向，無有是處。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於過去佛及弟子眾諸功德等取相分別隨喜迴向，諸佛世尊皆不隨喜。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是故菩薩摩訶薩眾欲於諸佛及諸弟子功德善根，正發隨喜迴向無上正等菩提，不應於中起有所得取相分別隨喜迴向。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於其中起有所得取相分別隨喜迴向，佛不說彼有大義利。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b28_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是隨喜迴向之心妄想分別，名雜毒故。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794b29_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如有飲食，雖具上妙色香美味而雜毒藥，愚夫淺識貪取噉之，初雖適意歡喜快樂，而後食消備受眾苦，或便致死若近失命。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是一類補特伽羅，不善受持，不善觀察甚深般若波羅蜜多文句義理，不善讀誦，不善通達甚深義趣，而告大乘種性者曰：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『來！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝於過去未來現在諸佛世尊戒蘊、定蘊、慧蘊、解脫蘊、解脫智見蘊，及餘無量無邊功德；",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若佛弟子於諸佛所種諸善根；",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若佛世尊授諸菩薩無上正等大菩提記，彼諸菩薩所種善根；",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若佛世尊授諸獨覺及聲聞記，彼有情類所種善根；",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c11_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸天人、阿素洛等於諸佛所乃至正法未滅盡來所種善根；",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人等所種善根，及有於他所成功德發生隨喜迴向善根。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c14_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是一切合集稱量，現前隨喜，與諸有情平等共有迴向無上正等菩提。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』如是所說隨喜迴向，以有所得取相分別而為方便。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如世間雜毒飲食初益後損故，此非善隨喜迴向。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以有所得取相分別，發起隨喜迴向之心，皆雜毒故。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩種性補特伽羅，不應隨彼所說而學。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是故，大德！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應說云何住菩薩乘善男子等，應於三世十方諸佛及弟子等功德善根隨喜迴向，可說名為無毒妙善隨喜迴向？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」具壽善現答慈氏言：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「住菩薩乘善男子等行深般若波羅蜜多，欲不謗佛而發隨喜迴向心者，應作是念：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『如諸如來、應、正等覺無障佛眼，通達遍知功德善根有如是性、有如是相、有如是法而可隨喜，我今亦應如是隨喜；",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0794c28_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如諸如來、應、正等覺無障佛眼，通達遍知應以如是諸福業事，迴向無上正等菩提，我今亦應如是迴向。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』住菩薩乘諸善男子、善女人等，於諸如來、應、正等覺及弟子等功德善根，應作如是隨喜迴向。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若作如是隨喜迴向則不謗佛，諸佛世尊同所隨喜。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩摩訶薩如是隨喜迴向之心，不雜眾毒離諸過咎，名正名善隨喜迴向，稱真法界，意樂勝解俱善圓滿。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，大士！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "住菩薩乘諸善男子、善女人等行深般若波羅蜜多，於諸如來、應、正等覺及弟子等功德善根，應作如是隨喜迴向：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a10_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『如佛戒蘊、定蘊、慧蘊、解脫蘊、解脫智見蘊及諸餘法，不墮三界非三世攝，隨喜迴向亦應如是。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如彼諸法自性空故，不墮三界非三世攝，隨喜迴向亦復如是。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a14_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂諸如來自性空故，不墮三界非三世攝；",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a15_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛功德自性空故，不墮三界非三世攝；",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聲聞、獨覺及人、天等自性空故，不墮三界非三世攝；",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸善根自性空故，不墮三界非三世攝；",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於彼隨喜自性空故，不墮三界非三世攝；",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所迴向法自性空故，不墮三界非三世攝；",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能迴向者自性空故，不墮三界非三世攝。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a21_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』若菩薩摩訶薩行深般若波羅蜜多時，如實了知諸法性相，不墮三界非三世攝。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不墮三界非三世攝，即不可以彼有相為方便、有所得為方便，發生隨喜迴向無上正等菩提。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a25_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以一切法自性不生，若法不生則無所有，不可以彼無所有法隨喜迴向，無所有故，是菩薩摩訶薩如是隨喜迴向無上正等菩提，不雜眾毒無所失壞名大迴向，無墮無攝，稱真法界，究竟圓滿。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795a29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「住菩薩乘諸善男子、善女人等，若以有相而為方便，或有所得而為方便，於諸如來及弟子等功德善根，發生隨喜迴向之心，當知是邪隨喜迴向。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此邪隨喜迴向之心，諸佛世尊所不稱讚。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩行深般若波羅蜜多時，作如是念：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『如十方界一切如來、應、正等覺如實通達功德善根有如是法，可依此法發生無倒隨喜迴向。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今亦應依如是法發生隨喜，迴向無上正等菩提，是為正發隨喜迴向。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』由斯定證無上菩提，轉妙法輪饒益一切。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b10_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊讚善現曰：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善哉！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b11_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今乃能為諸菩薩摩訶薩等作大佛事。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝為菩薩摩訶薩等宣說無倒隨喜迴向，如諸如來、應、正等覺通達遍知諸善根等有如是性、有如是相、有如是法，發生無倒隨喜迴向。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是隨喜迴向之心，稱真法界，究竟圓滿，汝今乃能如實宣說。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現當知！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人等，方便教化殑伽沙數三千大千世界有情，皆令安住十善業道所獲功德，是菩薩摩訶薩所起無倒隨喜迴向，於彼功德為最為勝、為尊為高、為妙為微妙、為上為無上、無等無等等。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "且置令住十善業道。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人等，方便教化殑伽沙數三千大千世界有情，皆令安住四靜慮、四無量、四無色定、五神通所獲功德，是菩薩摩訶薩所起無倒隨喜迴向，於彼功德為最為勝、為尊為高、為妙為微妙、為上為無上、無等無等等。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b27_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "且置令住四靜慮等。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795b28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人等，方便教化殑伽沙數三千大千世界有情，皆令安住預流果、或一來果、或不還果、或阿羅漢果、或獨覺菩提所獲功德，是菩薩摩訶薩所起無倒隨喜迴向，於彼功德，為最為勝、為尊為高、為妙為微妙、為上為無上、無等無等等。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "且置令住預流果等。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使如是殑伽沙數三千大千世界有情，皆成預流、一來、不還、阿羅漢果、獨覺菩提所有功德，是菩薩摩訶薩所起無倒隨喜迴向，於彼功德為最為勝、為尊為高、為妙為微妙、為上為無上、無等無等等。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "且置如是預流果等所有功德。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使十方殑伽沙數三千大千世界有情，皆發無上正等覺心。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "設有十方殑伽沙數三千大千世界有情，一一於彼諸菩薩所，皆以上妙衣服、飲食、臥具、醫藥及無量種上妙樂具，經如殑伽沙數大劫，以有所得而為方便，供養恭敬、尊重讚歎，於意云何？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸有情由此因緣得福多不？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」善現答言：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「甚多！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "甚多！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c17_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善逝！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是福聚若有形色，十方各如殑伽沙界不能容受。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告善現：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c19_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c19_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如汝所說。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c19_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩乘諸善男子、善女人等，於諸如來、應、正等覺及弟子等功德善根，發起無倒隨喜迴向，所獲功德甚多於前無量無數算數譬喻所不能及。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此菩薩乘善男子等所起無倒隨喜迴向，以無所得而為方便，甚深般若波羅蜜多方便善巧所攝受故，稱法界故，最勝無比。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c26_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸有情所獲福聚，以有所得為方便故，於此所起隨喜迴向，百分不及一，千分不及一，乃至鄔波尼殺曇分亦不及一。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0795c28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，四大天王各與眷屬二萬天子俱，頂禮佛足，合掌恭敬白言：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0796a01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0796a01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩摩訶薩所起無倒隨喜迴向，以無所得而為方便，甚深般若波羅蜜多方便善巧所攝受故，威力廣大稱真法界，疾能證得一切智智，勝前所說有所得施，無量倍數不可為比。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0796a05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時，天帝釋乃至他化自在天王，各與眷屬十萬天子俱，皆持種種天妙華鬘、塗散等香、衣服、瓔珞、寶幢、幡蓋、眾妙、珍奇，奏天樂音以奉施佛，供養恭敬、尊重讚歎，頂禮佛足，合掌白言：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0796a09_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是菩薩摩訶薩所起無倒隨喜迴向，以無所得而為方便，甚深般若波羅蜜多方便善巧所攝受故，威力廣大稱真法界，疾能證得一切智智，勝前所說有所得施，無量倍數不可為比。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0796a13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時，大梵天廣說乃至色究竟天各與無量百千天眾，前詣佛所，頂禮佛足，合掌恭敬俱發聲言：",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0796a16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「希有！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0796a16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0796a16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "甚奇！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0796a16_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善逝！",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0796a16_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩摩訶薩所起無倒隨喜迴向，以無所得而為方便，甚深般若波羅蜜多方便善巧所攝受故，威力廣大稱真法界，疾能證得一切智智，勝前所說有所得施，無量倍數不可為比。",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0796a20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」大般若波羅蜜多經卷第五百四十三",
        "from": "T07n0220d_543:0796a21_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]